Java is a high-level, object-oriented, general-purpose programming language 

We can use Java to make:

Mobile apps (like Android apps)
Websites
Games
Software for computers and businesses

  
A Simple Java Code Example:

  
public class Hello {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, world!");
    }
}

It Prints "Hello World!" on the screen
